data.description: Stunning 8 Bedroom, 6 Bath Home with Breathtaking views of both Iao Valley and Haleakala! Welcome to your dream oasis nestled in the heart of paradise! This magnificent 8-bedroom, 6-bathroom home is a true gem, offering unparalleled beauty, spaciousness, and endless possibilities. Situated on an expansive 12,142 sqft. lot, this property provides room for your imagination to run wild. 33 solar panels are a bonus necessity in this home. The interior is approximately 4,076 sqft., providing generous room sizes and open living spaces. Spectacular views of the famous Haleakala Mountain greet you each day, while the vast expanse of the ocean stretches as far as the eye can see. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a piece of paradise with limitless potential. Schedule a viewing and embark on a journey to make this dream property your very own! Current FHA Loan is assumable for qualified buyers.
